list.name: Changes
list.comment:
feat: add CRUD endpoints for sandwiches table
- Added POST /sandwiches/ to create a new sandwich - Added GET /sandwiches/ to retrieve all sandwiches - Added GET /sandwiches/{sandwich_id} to retrieve a specific sandwich by ID - Added PUT /sandwiches/{sandwich_id} to update a sandwich by ID - Added DELETE /sandwiches/{sandwich_id} to delete a sandwich by ID
These endpoints provide full CRUD functionality for managing sandwiches in the system.
